%e A394661   n=8:  2, 10, 9;
%e A394661   n=9:  4, 22, 22, 1;
%e A394661   n=10: 2, 44, 93, 26;
%e A394661   n=11: 6, 96, 289, 160, 1.
%e A394661 Row n=7: of the 7 prime knots with 7 crossings, 2 have genus 1 (7_2, 7_4), 4 have genus 2 (7_3, 7_5, 7_6, 7_7), and 1 has genus 3 (the (2,7) torus knot 7_1).
